{"tid":2259591,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"警認不出「九尾妖狐」 毒販譏笑：沒看《火影》喔","createTime":"2020-10-27T03:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T04:59:12.000Z","uid":20738,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f003d7b9b646debcfb7c2dc2cc070f81742ea87b","tid":2259591,"uid":20738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:05:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2585221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2585221&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETc0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=9cd80fa0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2585221&h=f7b25009\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2585221</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方抄到數包火影忍者毒咖啡，但警員沒看過《火影》，反被毒嫌譏笑。（記者王捷翻攝）<br />\n<br />\n2018/10/18 23:13<br />\n〔記者王捷／台南報導〕台南警方上個月抄到印有《火影忍者》的毒咖啡，沒想到這個月又有「火影」現蹤。上個月警方問持毒嫌犯《火影》主角名字、第幾代火影？毒嫌答不出來，因而露餡。這次警方在林姓藥頭家中查獲400多公克、多種口味的毒品咖啡包，其中就有數包「火影毒咖啡」，不過，這是換警員不識《火影》，將毒咖啡包裝上的「九尾妖狐」認成「獅子頭」，被藥頭譏笑：「啊警察是不是沒看《火影》喔？」<br />\n<br />\n《火影忍者》是日本漫畫家岸本齊史創作的少年漫畫，被簡稱為「火影」，講述主角漩渦鳴人在虛構的忍者世界中，用自身九尾妖狐的力量，一步步成長，最終成為故鄉火之國木葉忍者村的首領，第七代火影。<br />\n<br />\n《火影》雖然已經完結，但仍是主流少年漫畫，連毒品咖啡包也印有鳴人、九尾的畫面。台南警方在上個月攔查到一名男子持有「火影毒咖啡」，問了火影主角的名字與主角是第幾代火影，嫌疑人答不出來，當場露餡。<br />\n<br />\n警方這個月也在林姓女藥頭家中出一堆毒品，其中有印著鳴人與九尾的毒咖啡，警方登記毒品種類時，請林女配合說出各種口味的毒咖啡名稱，但查緝警員沒看過火影動漫，將妖狐看成獅子，問林女「火影毒咖啡」的俗稱是否叫「獅子頭」？沒想到換來林女譏笑。<br />\n<br />\n林女說，這包毒咖啡就俗稱「火影」，上個月得知有人買火影被抓，很多藥頭都以為警方有在看《火影》，沒看過《火影》的藥腳，也把主角名字、第幾代首領熟記，她還以為警察都有在看火影。訊後警方將林女依毒品危害防制條例移送。"},{"pid":"2a1480eca7aff68a24014e02a48bee181fb53c98","tid":2259591,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:10:29.000Z","msg":"火影咖啡"},{"pid":"850c85908b550db1184f2d94a2ced33dcd6bcc5f","tid":2259591,"uid":357759,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:22:39.000Z","msg":"火影世界第一"},{"pid":"1bec9cd49ad543bfe82f3576ebc25429e858f61b","tid":2259591,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:25:07.000Z","msg":"一樂老闆轉行賣咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e410160130fc1754efa6e8923b0a099099ec1339","tid":2259591,"uid":36915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:36:25.000Z","msg":"鳩蛇去撚左邊"},{"pid":"a90db6faa5ec0e7aad0694a1e36898eba82a9480","tid":2259591,"uid":116910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:39:28.000Z","msg":"問火影第幾代答唔出個到笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf926dd98a1263f110603deeafd685ce33dd5654","tid":2259591,"uid":83328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2018/10/18/2585221_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F2585221_1.jpg&h=eb59302d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鳴人個樣都好似中咗毒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b36409d420d56b9842314568cf4ba31720560a","tid":2259591,"uid":116143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T04:41:59.000Z","msg":"但仍是<span class=\"red\">主流</span>少年漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e856430310082c713eb1ee019ea41cdeb17b6178","tid":2259591,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"比套火影我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}